title: Episode 367: Love is Around the Corner (Feat. Tink & Hitmaka)
itunes:title: Episode 367: Love is Around the Corner (Feat. Tink & Hitmaka)
description:
Artist, Tink & Producer, Hitmaka join the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote Tink's upcoming "Pillow Talk" album. The crew discuss the process of making the album together, all the trifling things guys do to women, borrowing your rich friends stuff to flex, and much more. Tink & Hitmaka shy away from confirming their relationship but leave clues throughout the episode that really make you wonder...enjoy!
